### Revoke Consent

**POST** `/api/v1/consent/revoke`

Revoke an existing consent.

**Headers:**

- `Authorization: Bearer <jwt_token>` (Principal auth)

**Request Body:**

```json
{
  "consent_id": "660e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440001",
  "reason": "No longer want promotional emails",
